yle=&quot;word-break: break-all; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 5px; font-size: 1.1vw; vertical-align: middle; border-style: solid; border-color: gainsboro; border-width: 1px;&quot; height=&quot;40&quot;&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1.75em;&quot;&gt;热导率/W·(m·K)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td bgcolor=&quot;#FFFFFF&quot; valign=&quot;top&quot; width=&quot;20%&quot; style=&quot;word-break: break-all; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 5px; font-size: 1.1vw; vertical-align: middle; border-style: solid; border-color: gainsboro; border-width: 1px;&quot; height=&quot;40&quot;&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1.75em;&quot;&gt;17&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td bgcolor=&quot;#FFFFFF&quot; valign=&quot;top&quot; width=&quot;20%&quot; style=&quot;word-break: break-all; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 5px; font-size: 1.1vw; vertical-align: middle; border-style: solid; border-color: gainsboro; border-width: 1px;&quot; height=&quot;40&quot;&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1.75em;&quot;&gt;212&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td bgcolor=&quot;#FFFFFF&quot; valign=&quot;top&quot; width=&quot;20%&quot; style=&quot;word-break: break-all; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 5px; font-size: 1.1vw; vertical-align: middle; border-style: solid; border-color: gainsboro; border-width: 1px;&quot; height=&quot;40&quot;&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1.75em;&quot;&gt;85&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td bgcolor=&quot;#FFFFFF&quot; valign=&quot;top&quot; width=&quot;20%&quot; style=&quot;word-break: break-all; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 5px; font-size: 1.1vw; vertical-align: middle; border-style: solid; border-color: gainsboro; border-width: 1px;&quot; height=&quot;40&quot;&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1.75em;&quot;&gt;255&lt;br style=&quot;word-break: break-all; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;&quot;/&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; list-style: none; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: break-all; text-size-adjust: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.75em;&quot;&gt;　　钛的热导率小，仅为钢的1/5,铝的1/13,铜的1/25。导热性不好是钛的一个缺点，但在某些场合下可以利用钛的这一特征。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; list-style: none; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: break-all; text-size-adjust: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.75em;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;word-break: break-all; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;&quot;&gt;　　7、弹性模量小&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;word-break: break-all; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;table align=&quot;center&quot; bgcolor=&quot;#000000&quot; cellpadding=&quot;0&quot; cellspacing=&quot;1&quot; class=&quot;p_biaoge&quot; width=&quot;100%&quot;&gt;&lt;tbody style=&quot;word-break: break-all; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;tr class=&quot;firstRow&quot; style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; list-style: none; word-break: break-all;&quot;&gt;&lt;td bgcolor=&quot;#FFFFFF&quot; valign=&quot;top&quot; width=&quot;25%&quot; style=&quot;word-break: break-all; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 5px; font-size: 1.1vw; vertical-align: middle; border-style: solid; border-color: gainsboro; border-width: 1px;&quot; height=&quot;40&quot;&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1.75em;&quot;&gt;金属&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td bgcolor=&quot;#FFFFFF&quot; valign=&quot;top&quot; width=&quot;25%&quot; style=&quot;word-break: break-all; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 5px; font-size: 1.1vw; vertical-align: middle; border-style: solid; border-color: gainsboro; border-width: 1px;&quot; height=&quot;40&quot;&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1.75em;&quot;&gt;Ti&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td bgcolor=&quot;#FFFFFF&quot; valign=&quot;top&quot; width=&quot;25%&quot; style=&quot;word-break: break-all; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 5px; font-size: 1.1vw; vertical-align: middle; border-style